{"id":188344,"type":1,"name":"ふたがしら","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/14/a9/188344_Dr01o.jpg","summary":"時は江戸時代。盗賊“赤目一味”の頭目・辰五郎は、死に際に弁蔵と宗次の2人の手を取り、一味のことを託して息を引き取った。\r\nだが、2人以外に辰五郎の言葉を聞いたものはおらず、姐さんが辰五郎直筆の遺言を出してきたため、跡目は辰五郎の弟分である甚三郎が継ぐことになった。最期の言葉を反故にされ、納得のいかない弁蔵と宗次は、一味を離れ「でっかいことをやる」ために旅に出る。","info":"<li><span>册数: </span>既刊7卷</li><li><span>作者: </span><a href=\"/person/3734\">オノ・ナツメ</a></li><li><span>出版社: </span><a href=\"/person/6749\">小学館</a></li><li><span>连载杂志: </span><a href=\"/person/8550\">月刊IKKI</a>（2011年7月号至2014年11月号）→<a href=\"/person/17946\">ヒバナ</a>（2015年3月）</li>","collection":{"wish":2,"collect":1,"on_hold":1},"tags":[{"name":"漫画系列","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":3734,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/c8/21/3734_prsn_aHY0e.jpg","name":"小野夏芽","desc":"作者"},{"id":6749,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/2c/ec/6749_prsn_O9b2I.jpg","name":"小学馆","desc":"出版社"},{"id":8550,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/9f/15/8550_prsn_Y1Ggd.jpg","name":"月刊IKKI","desc":"连载杂志"},{"id":17946,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/a4/24/17946_prsn_9gg7k.jpg","name":"ヒバナ","desc":"连载杂志"}],"relations":[{"id":130151,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/dd/00/130151_uii5g.jpg","title":"ふたがしら","type":"三次元","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/130151"},{"id":164517,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/09/39/164517_pyEcD.jpg","title":"ふたがしら2","type":"三次元","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/164517"}],"comic":[{"id":188335,"name":"ふたがしら (1)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/4e/30/188335_jp.jpg"},{"id":188336,"name":"ふたがしら (2)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/0b/e5/188336_jp.jpg"},{"id":188337,"name":"ふたがしら (3)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/b4/d3/188337_jp.jpg"},{"id":188338,"name":"ふたがしら (4)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/cd/d0/188338_jp.jpg"},{"id":188339,"name":"ふたがしら (5)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/6d/05/188339_jp.jpg"},{"id":188340,"name":"ふたがしら (6)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/16/e0/188340_jp.jpg"},{"id":188341,"name":"ふたがしら (7)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/89/85/188341_2o26m.jpg"}